<h2 id="using-dropdown">Using dropdown</h2>

<p>Dropdown should only be used if there is no other alternative as some users can struggle with the functionality.</p>

<p>Try using the <a href="radio">radio</a> or <a href="checkbox">checkbox</a> elements instead.</p>

<p>Itâ€™s often used when there is a long list that canâ€™t presented in another way, such as a list of countries or languages.</p>

